    "content": "<p>In a world which celebrates righteous violence, of storming capitols, kidnappings, beheadings, of intoxicating hatreds, we so easily dismiss the difficult wisdom of the man Martin Luther King called his \u201cguiding light,\u201d Mohandas Gandhi, that freedom won by the blood of others is freedom not worth having. And it is not freedom.  <a href=\"https://mastodon.online/tags/MLKDay2024\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>MLKDay2024</span></a></p><p>In honor of <a href=\"https://mastodon.online/tags/MLKDay\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>MLKDay</span></a>, we are making our film The Best Democracy Money Can Buy available as a FREE DOWNLOAD (or with a donation): <a href=\"https://www.gregpalast.com/best-democracy-free-or-donate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">gregpalast.com/best-democracy-</span><span class=\"invisible\">free-or-donate/</span></a></p>",
